Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以笔名“芥川竹人”出道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人在背地里议论
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在同一个教室而已就有女生大叫起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种数不胜数的难听的别名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是地狱般的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:03:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在奇迹般的能享受着高中生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为在这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立闪学园高中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是汇集全国天才级精英高中生的学园
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:17.05,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁坊回  器械体操天才
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,品味  肉体  头脑  如风般自由的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:21.85,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红牡丹  前卫艺术天才
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其潜在可能性可谓是无限大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交际  常识  道德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是世上怎样的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:28.01,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾线兰  编程天才
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都无法阻止其才能之奔流
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:33.36,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名机来夏  摄影天才
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其理由正是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们和她们正是与生俱来的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:38.11,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円修律  数学天才
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有请学园创办者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长兼理事长的黑树水墨先生发言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百分之九十九的汗水与百分之一的灵感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换言之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信灵感战斗到最后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有灵感的努力可谓是无用功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世人说些什么都不要去在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪学园校训
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信灵感  相信感性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贯彻自己的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿荣光与闪学园同在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上  由木谷星报道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:21.78,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木谷星  解说天才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是天才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才也会有失败的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  丈途
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的同学兼朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也尝试着以我的方式去理解你的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被班里不了解实情的女生毫无道理地误会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太不注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途  你有在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被表面的厌恶感与道德感蒙蔽了眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有看到真相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性才是人类的源泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,描写性就是描写人的本质
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  这才是我的文学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用工口作家的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终有一天登上文学的巅峰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我的文学会在大家的心里…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  在给文学史刻下不朽不灭的印记的这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界将会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻正是反击那些嘲笑我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为光荣的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是佐治亚州
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.74,0:06:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在南国小岛与美女们相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的后宫生活各种充实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  丈途
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:06:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睫毛好长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  有在听呢  有在听呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错呢  喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢才是问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你冷不防地说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是你的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来  律
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惯例的  惯例的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3.1415926535897932384626…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然让人感觉很COOL
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却是个认真的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么偶尔会说些莫名其妙的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  姐姐大人  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱做的炸虾其美味程度能响彻银河呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  以前律好像有说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常甜美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人  好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的“蜜”又如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  我倒是不会对别人的兴趣指手画脚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看什么看  真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说等等  兰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撇开抱怨不说  没那样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途对你做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视线啊  工口视线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定又在脑补些那方面的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说  我们的关系可没好到直呼其名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是特异功能的天才吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望你能理论一点地回答问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律  对你的友情我表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我的确妄想了  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部  部长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么部长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新闻同好会的部长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪学园最高年级有名的天才哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途同学  下周的头版新闻已经确定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一年级生特辑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家请关注这位天才
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首个“单簧管天才”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣唐吹音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小吹音?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的取材对像从我们班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真让人感兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  部长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉  这次让我去取材有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.26,0:10:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有  也好像没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个  部长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教室里  音乐大楼里都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有回宿舍  那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是热心呢  芥川丈途
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直像尾行狂人一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾行BOY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.49,0:10:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是新闻同好会的取材啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是个万能说辞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:10:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  痞子绅士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说为什么你会跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是新闻同好会的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍照的技术我可是一流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点都不明白么  色色脑袋君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看得更透彻些吧  真正的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的人类?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满欲望的那丑陋的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那一瞬间才能看清真正的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手  你这臭虫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄像师可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  今晚你是摄像素材
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心灵的一面  决定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}我的眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那表情还真不错呢  你这卑鄙贱人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人发狂似的把红黑色的凶器插进了洞里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  溢出了快乐的“汁”水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那比岩浆更热  比奶油更甜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着伴随而来的是罪恶般的苦味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后女摄影师…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  住口  别读
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  以我为原型在妄想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  保持这个样子就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会放过本能爆发的瞬间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在扭扭捏捏什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧  废物色情君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都怪谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这的确是机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是踌躇的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我想与鸣唐同学说上话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地说上话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  好好道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:21.43,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶像歌手天才  园声谣江
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能掉以轻心的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这都没有找到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.91,0:13:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来  别过来  别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开  让开  让开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:20.99,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发明天才  香学创
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输出力应该足够了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是平衡的问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之再调整下翅膀的设计…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?  这是什么  是胡桃么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道很香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么是湿的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…在…干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子有点饿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且因为睡眠不足  在发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹音的…簧片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要吃!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go Go 闪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go 闪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我在这儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…和鸣唐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么能看呆了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是好机会  来夏也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人可以好好谈谈  不是很简单吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这感觉是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下  停下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.06,0:17:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我写了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这  不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.81,0:18:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明在眼前躺着个毫无防备的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该遵循本能像饿猪一样扑上去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上  突击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气扑上去  思春期蠢猪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也算不健全的思春期男性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我知道廉耻  你这自慰男
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要比喻的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是最为纯净的一滴水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金的水滴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抑或是  春天的生机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽和愉快凝聚而成的水润的宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要念  不许念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不对劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是那种女人的森林啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又黑又亮的肉枪之类的  群X之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样的  你脑子坏了吗  丈途
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:18:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 在乱说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:19:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌辱  蹂躏  阴阜  跟着复述
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找回真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌辱  蹂躏  阴阜  念!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会跟着念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌辱  蹂躏  阴阜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  你啊  嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又  又来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣唐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那  那  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.88,0:20:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣唐同学  等…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后也没能取材啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止从未有过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平时的感觉不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有能量很有冲击性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很令人舒畅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加的…怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在脑子里翻来覆去地想也没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:20:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是作家  要做的事只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用魔法单簧管变身咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pulalila Pulinda Pululupi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会输给邪恶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是魔法少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pu la li la   Pu lu lu pi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我在写轻小说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.02,0:21:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  部长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途同学  原稿写好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.18,0:21:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是有原因的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.77,0:21:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来部长为什么会在男生宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.88,0:21:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没写好也是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:22:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会等到你写出好东西的  芥川老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.56,0:22:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.45,0:22:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我会这么说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.71,0:22:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次

